Syntax: say <message>
Syntax: ' <message

A generic way to communicate with other people in <h>.
Some rooms will prevent these commands due to a magical dweomer of silence.

Say shows the text to everyone in the room.  You can use ' as a shorthand
notation for "say".
   EX: say hello world
       ' hello world

See Also: ASK, TELL, SHOUT, WHISPER, COLOR STRINGS
Related Topics: COMMUNICATIONS
